import {Route, BrowserRouter as Router, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Navbar from '../layout/Navbar'
import Agendamento from '../componts/agendconsul'


function Rotas (){

    return(
        <Router>
            <Navbar />

            <Routes>
                <Route path='/' element={<Agendamento />}/>
                
            </Routes>
        </Router>

    )
}

export default Rotas
